::Ramulus::

A beep distracts Ramulus from his thoughts, the scanner at his side alerting 
of a newly detected bot. He looks down on it, frowning. The same bot he had 
shot down earlier was active again, near another one.

Ramulus spins around. The Alliance could wait if a life was at stake! Taking 
off at full speed, Ramulus runs north, heading for DeathScythe's location.
